            <thetext>When one item is preselected due to the selection API and the user now try to select a range by mouse (press shift/mouse down). The multi selection is wrong, it starts always on the first item, not on the preselected item.

Here the code to reproduce the issue:
http://tinyurl.com/33bm867

1. load the application.
2. try to select the &quot;Item No 7&quot; by using the mouse when pressing shift key.

You will see that the selection starts from the first item &quot;Item No 1&quot; and not from item &quot;Item No 3&quot;. This is not correct, the selection should be started from the preselected item &quot;Item No 3&quot;.</thetext>
